Not certified .. Dora comments on the death of Haitham Ahmed Zaki
07 Nov 2019, 03:01 by Mustafa Karam
Mustafa Karam called the artist Dora the artist Haitham Ahmed Zaki, the son of the late artist Ahmed Zaki, who passed away today and the cause of death has not yet been determined. I can hardly believe your early departure .. heartache .. God bless you, my friend, my good heart and make your paradise .. And be in a place more merciful and better .. And mercy your great father Ahmed Zaki and your beautiful mother Hala Fouad. Comments came with prayers and mercy on him and came between "survival of God and our Lord have mercy on him and forgive him and live in paradise" and God bless his mercy ğŸ˜¢ God bless his mercy Lord, and "God have mercy" and "there is no power but God, God bless his soul and forgive him Roomy. "
